	=====================================================================================
	DATALIST FILE
	Defines example datalists.
	=====================================================================================
	A datalist file can define one or more datalists. A datalist contains items
	which in turn contain several datalist item properties and may contain one or more
	datalist item sets (wrapped in the <sets> tag). Datalist item sets can contain a
	list of key-value pairs.
